<ul><li>A <a href="/wiki/Convex_function" title="Convex function">convex function</a> <span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle f_{0}(x):\mathbb {R} ^{n}\to \mathbb {R} }">
