</p><p>Finally, we require the existence of a <a href="/wiki/Separation_oracle" title="Separation oracle">separation oracle</a> for the convex set <i><span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle Q}">
