  </semantics>
</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/16cfa10329afdb784e9e4a112a3a8a7a71a6a0be" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -2.505ex; width:52.967ex; height:6.176ex;" alt="{\displaystyle {\mathcal {E}}^{(k)}=\left\{x\in \mathbb {R} ^{n}\ :\ \left(x-x^{(k)}\right)^{T}P_{(k)}^{-1}\left(x-x^{(k)}\right)\leqslant 1\right\}.}"></span></dd></dl>
<p>We query the cutting-plane oracle to obtain a vector <span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle g^{(k+1)}\in \mathbb {R} ^{n}}">
